{"tid":1281457,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國被指秘密安裝手機程式　監控新疆遊客","createTime":"2019-07-03T09:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T10:01:57.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4b2ea822382831e41f2ff40df20f04ee0b4d99ed","tid":1281457,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:44:19.000Z","msg":"英國《衛報》、德國《南德意志報》和美國《紐約時報》一項共同調查發現，遊客從中亞國家入境中國新疆，交手機予中國邊防人員檢查時，手機會被秘密安裝名叫「蜂采」的應用程式，程式可截取郵件、短信、聯繫人，以及手機本身的信息。<br />\n<br />\n根據《衛報》，學者和網絡安全專家分析，這款由中國公司設計的應用程序截取大量中國當局認爲有問題的内容，包括與伊斯蘭極端主義和西藏流亡精神領袖達賴喇嘛相關内容。<br />\n<br />\n大多數情况下，手機被退還給遊客時，該應用程式已被卸載。<br />\n（《衛報》/美國之音）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/article/20190703/s00004/1562136208863/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BC%8F-%E7%9B%A3%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2Farticle%2F20190703%2Fs00004%2F1562136208863%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25A7%2598%25E5%25AF%2586%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%25A3%259D%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%25BC%258F-%25E7%259B%25A3%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2596%2586%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%25AE%25A2&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV9w%2Be0OQbTcODApWAJdetE8%3D&h=a23d2e05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2Farticle%2F20190703%2Fs00004%2F1562136208863%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25A7%2598%25E5%25AF%2586%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%25A3%259D%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%25BC%258F-%25E7%259B%25A3%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2596%2586%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%25AE%25A2&h=bb4736ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/article/20190703/s00004/1562136208863/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A2%AB